  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d72d98cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F15Dz37YtAkuMKAo99BwM35Fak2NMnJDa27stKyFiaAWowTTt9uuohibzMUdLC3icBGDrbS54twoXejn2UN4E0qFsKAMLAA7wjn315hhaRiajHibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0px; width: 100%;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:0px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n       <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 16px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">想象一下这个场景：你在地铁上刷着 Slack，看到一个需要修复的 bug。你点一个 emoji 表情，等到了办公室，代码已经写好、测试通过，Pull Request 等着你审查。这不是科幻小说，这是 Stripe 工程师每天的真实工作状态。更震撼的是，Stripe 每周有大约 1300 个代码合并请求完全由 AI agent 完成，工程师只负责审查，一行代码都不用自己写。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 16px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我第一次听到这个数字时，我的反应是：这怎么可能？1300 个 PR，每周？要知道很多小型工程团队一个月可能都合并不了这么多代码。但当我深入了解 Stripe 的 Minions 系统后，我意识到这不仅可能，而且代表着软件工程的一个根本性转变。我们正在从\"工程师写代码\"转向\"工程师管理 AI 写代码\"，这个转变的速度比我想象的要快得多。</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 92%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.45740740740740743\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" width=\"100%\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eacc0f18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F15Dz37YtAkt2nWkTEfSPwmHWRxCxf1iaauKiaDkkAp5oHkHNxZRjQsYxNo0ibLLofljtFrf9hV8aqGibkAoZFwBicN2ibwXNzsk4GMFz5SSvcibjLU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 16px;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stripe 的软件工程师 Steve Kaliski 在最近的一次访谈中分享了他们如何构建和使用这套系统。Steve 在 Stripe 工作了六年半，一直专注于开发者工具和支付基础设施的建设。他提到一个非常有意思的观察：\"我已经不记得上次是从文本编辑器开始工作是什么时候了。\"他的工作通常从 Google 文档、Jira 工单或者 Slack 对话开始，这些才是更自然的工作起点。等到需要真正动手写代码或做最后调整时，才会进入文本编辑器。这种工作方式的转变，让启动一项工作的激活能量大大降低。</span></p>\n     <div class=\"custom_select_card_wrp\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;text-decoration-line:none;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;widows:2;\">\n      <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;text-decoration-line:none;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">PS：我的出海新书已经上架了，我特意申请了公众号读者专属的优惠链接，可以享受半价折扣，欢迎感兴趣的朋友购买。</span></p>\n      <p class=\"custom_select_card_wrp\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:auto;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;text-decoration-line:none;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:solid;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;widows:2;\"><mp-common-product data-cardtype=\"1\" data-windowproduct=\"FSvHaRwFTYFW_OxhO7CEhOQsIhySRu3Lyeqr6WxntCICfWkCH9Y-Y-gGN8xX2DEi_zPcg2rEA5THpkiu2Eo3-RWO\" data-title=\"出海：产品全球化营销实践\" data-type=\"0\" class=\"custom_select_card mp_common_widget\" data-immutable=\"1\" data-req-scene=\"2\" has-insert-preloading=\"1\" data-url-params=\"{&quot;article_info&quot;:&quot;eyJtcF9iaXoiOiIzODc0NzYyNDEyIiwiaXRlbV9pZHgiOjEsImFwcG1zZ2lkIjoyMjQ3NDk0MTA1LCJpdGVtX3Nob3dfdHlwZSI6MCwibXBfYXJ0aWNsZV9zY2VuZSI6MCwibXBfc3ViX3NjZW5lIjowLCJtcF9nZXRfYThrZXlfc2NlbmUiOjAsImNhcnJpZXJfdHlwZSI6MCwic2VhcmNoX2NsaWNrX2lkIjoiIn0=&quot;}\" link-id=\"00c2\" data-loaded=\"1\" style=\" color-scheme: initial;ruby-position: initial;writing-mode: initial;display: initial;font-family: initial;font-feature-settings: initial;font-kerning: initial;font-optical-sizing: initial;font-palette: initial;font-size: initial;font-size-adjust: initial;font-style: initial;font-synthesis-small-caps: initial;font-synthesis-style: initial;font-synthesis-weight: initial;font-variant-alternates: initial;font-variant-caps: initial;font-variant-east-asian: initial;font-variant-emoji: initial;font-variant-ligatures: initial;font-variant-numeric: initial;font-variant-position: initial;font-variation-settings: initial;font-weight: initial;font-width: initial;text-orientation: initial;text-rendering: initial;zoom: initial;-webkit-font-smoothing: initial;-webkit-locale: initial;-webkit-text-zoom: initial;letter-spacing: initial;text-spacing-trim: initial;word-spacing: initial;background: initial;mask: initial;accent-color: initial;place-content: initial;place-items: initial;place-self: initial;alignment-baseline: initial;anchor-name: initial;anchor-scope: initial;animation-composition: initial;animation: initial;appearance: initial;aspect-ratio: initial;backdrop-filter: initial;backface-visibility: initial;background-blend-mode: initial;baseline-shift: initial;line-clamp: initial;block-step: initial;border-collapse: initial;border: initial;box-shadow: initial;box-sizing: border-box !important;break-after: initial;break-before: initial;break-inside: initial;buffered-rendering: initial;caption-side: initial;caret-color: initial;clear: initial;clip: initial;clip-path: initial;clip-rule: initi